# NIX REGISTRY
Nixpkgs: nixpkgs.nix
Source: https://github.com/NixOS/nix
Description: Manage the flake registry (aliases for flake URLs).
Version: nix --version

## Commands

### Basics
- nix registry list: List all registered flake aliases.

### Essentials
- nix registry add my-nixpkgs github:NixOS/nixpkgs/nixos-unstable: Create a custom alias.
- nix registry remove my-nixpkgs: Delete an alias.

### Intermediaries
- nix registry pin nixpkgs: Lock an alias to its current version.

## Tips
- Allows using shorter names (like nixpkgs#) instead of full URLs.

